Altran Technologies SA, Microsoft Corp and Flight Focus Launch Electronic Flight Bag Solution for Aircraft Connectivity
Sunday, 16 Jun 2013 08:00pm EDT
Altran Technologies SA, Microsoft Corp and Flight Focus announced the launch of NavigaSuite, the first suite of Electronic Flight Bag (EFB) applications designed by Altran Technologies SA and integrated by Flight Focus on the Windows 8 platform. NavigaSuite is a flight deck soloution for pilots. Its features include pre-flight check in, workflow for missions, manuals and charts, as well as the possibility of selecting the data sets required in a clipboard, and sending messages to flight operations. The Mail App is automatically installed in Windows 8 and used as the official messaging tool for pilots and flight operations.Â 
